game.name: Princess Soup Kitchen
game.description:
Hey ladies! The funniest and highly exciting cooking session has just entered your way today. Would you like to take your seat here and enjoy the most immersive cooking experience? Join Princess Soup Kitchen game and be prepared to learn how to surprise your guests with the delicious soup by just following a few simple steps! No need to remember the measured ingredients or organic vegetables when you decide to give this brand new cooking game a try today! Follow the instructions to prepare your dish as fast as you can!

There are multiple ingredients like unicorn horns, bat wings and pot fresh frog legs to explore. Hurry up friends! The cute little princes is waiting for her favorite soup deliberately and your guidance can help taste it timely. Grab some fresh vegetables, vinegar, oil, flour, pasta, condiments, meat and some other useful ingredients to prepare your soup recipe! Choose the ingredients in your desired ratio and get ready to chop each one before adding it to the pot!

Once all your ingredients are mixed in the pot, make sure to stir it well and invite the cute girl to taste it. Take a moment and keep your eyes on her face when she reacts after tasking your super special soup in this HTML5 brand new game! Prepare multiple recipes and do hard work to grab all the 13 badges available in the game! Keep practicing until get the mastery in our soup cooking game!
